 upper limit on the GW waveform strength published and represents the first\nbroadband asteroseismology measurement using a GW detector.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Mar 2007 20:07:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 19 Apr 2007 18:29:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-08-27"}
