ata as a further test of our scaling method. We infer the\nvalue of BH mass of (15.6 +/- 1.5) M_Sun in this source which is consistent\nwith the previous BH mass estimate in GRS 1915 of (13.3 +/- 4) M_Sun. We obtain\nthe BH mass in Cyg X-1 in the range (8.7 +/- 0.8) M_Sun.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 16 Mar 2007 14:55:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-02-11"}
